content:
CrossFit WOD:
Strength:
Paused Front Squat
2-2-2-2-2
*2sec Pause at the bottom of the first rep of each set

Metcon:
AMRAP in 20min of:
5 Toes-to-bar
10 KB Deadlifts (#24/16,x2)
15 Pushups

Weightlifting:
Part 1:
7 sets:
2 Snatch Balance
1 OH Squat
50-70%

Part 2:
Deficit Snatch Pull
Deficit Snatch
5 x 1+2 60-65%
5 x 1+1 70-75%
5 x 0+1  80-85%

Part 3:
Clean Deadlift
Hang Clean
8 x 1+2  65-75%
5 x 1+1  80-95%

Part 4:
5 sets:
1 Push Jerk
2 Split Jerk
70-75% from jerk
